" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/happy.png" alt="Happy" title="Happy" /> that's one of the things I love about this forum: everyone has their own rules and stories for whatever the game left out, so there are nearly infinite different continuities to choose from! <img class="emoticon emoticon-happy" id="happy" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/happy.png" alt="Happy" title="Happy" />  If you want to connect your story with mine, I would advice you to wait until I've revealed more about the concerned things, but that's up to you.  I won't blame you if you decide not to, because it may take a while for me to cover this stuff, but if you decide not to wait you just run the risk of splitting into your own continuity (not that there's anything wrong with that <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" />)<BR /><BR /><BR />Now I noticed that some readers (although I'm hoping most of them are but just haven't said it) have been getting excited wondering about the mystery side of Crux Origins.  Well, all I am going to say is, at least for some of these secrets, there's not much time left to wait...<BR /><BR />...But on a related note, things have been getting pretty busy on my end, and that + slow moderation preventing adequate flow of information = high probability of increased waiting time before I can release the next chapter.  Believe me, I wish I could spend more time writing this, but it can't be helped <img class="emoticon emoticon-sad" id="sad" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/sad.png" alt="Sad" title="Sad" /><BR /><BR />Judging from the current pattern, by the time this gets approved it will probably be out of date <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />~~The Original Major~~ </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />Ok sorry it took so long for me to respond, i was sick for a week and then all this other stuff came up but i just wanted to say thanks and tell you that im going to just go ahead with my story. I also wanted to ask if i could do something that would help both of our stories. i wanted to know if i could tell in my story why  and how the  people that the major's family was with got pushed off the edge but like i said before i would not say anything about the major or his family unlees you said i could. any way it would make my story longer and help my plot a lot and  then you wouldent have to explain that (ok fine i guess i gain mostly from it<img class="emoticon emoticon-smile" id="smile" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/smile.png" alt="Smile" title="Smile" /> but i just was asking if i could do that. as soon as i post this i will post my story and if you say no to my idea its ok cause that part would come futher towds the end in my story. I also wanted to say this, i thing that you should seirusly consider becoming a writer when you get older. I mean you have a brillint mind when it comes to a plot and you know how to hold the people reading it in suspense. And the Major oh were do i begin, you take raw emotion and mold it into a charector that is just plain awesome. well i have to go typ up my story so when you can respond to me as fast as possible.<BR /><BR />ps. if you could, read my story when it comes out and let me know what to think. thx<BR /><BR />yours truly, starwars7495 aka lightningwarrior95<BR /><BR /><BR />~life is a lego set, open the possibilities~ </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! SO MANY ERRORS!!!!!! ok the last post on this quote (not the post im writeing now but the one above it) was going to be on the post you wrote about how you wish you could tell me more about the story so i could write something about the villige the majors familly was in that got pushed off of crux. I feel stupid. but i wont let it get me down, yet<img class="emoticon emoticon-smile" id="smile" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/smile.png" alt="Smile" title="Smile" />   Oh and chapter two is now up so if you could can you read it. It sadly as a lot of errors due to the fact the internet did not get turned on until 10:15pm so i was VERY sleepy. Chapter two i promise will be much better. im the minifig that can not write whatsoever who is writeing a story,<BR /><BR />yours truly, starwars7495 aka lightningwarrior95<BR /><BR />~life is a lego set, open the posibilities~ </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />Ahh, don't worry about what and what isn't quoted.  I can just figure it out by looking at the order you post them <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /><BR /><BR />And already you are making assumptions!!  When did I say anything about them being in a village? They could have lived in a city, or on a farm, or anywhere for all you know!! <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" />  <BR /><BR />If I tell you the secret, it will be on different topic, and inside Uber Jammers.  I might even just create a topic just so we can talk with maximum privacy.  But if I tell you the secret, I would expect you to keep that secret, and never do or say anything, ANYTHING, that could give it away.  Not to be judgemental or anything, but this would all be so much simpler if we just said you were writing from a separate continuity. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" />  You'll see what I mean if I really do bring myself to tell you.  I'm really beyond the point of turning back on this secret piece of the plot, and I don't want you or anyone to spoil it, so I really am torn here.<BR /><BR /><BR />If I asked everyone, and I mean EVERYONE, not to  peak if I put the secret in jammers on this topic, could I trust them?  I really don't want to spoil it for anyone, but if I must I would need to be sure that no one beyond those I wish to hear would spoil the secret for others or for themselves.  This would still apply if it was on another topic.  Please guys, I'm counting on you.  <BR /><BR /><BR />~~The Original Major~~ </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BLOCKQUOTE><BR />Sorry if i made you mad about the villige stuff, i was just useing it as an example. and on the secret, i would keep it if you told me. i know its hard trusting someone on the boards though, i mean i could be someone who is tying to get info out of you and ruin your story, just like you could be some jerk who is in real life a weird person. But im not trying to ruin you and get info (i hope you dont think of me like that) and you in my sight are a nice person who likes to be carefull with what he does and who he talks to, which is good. So i hope you could trust me but if you cant then ill understand. now on the part i want to use, i was going to use the villege, barn, city, ect ect, in a story that i would write after MYTHRAN ORIGINS called The wars of crux saga (it would talk about all the wars the jesters,bat lords, bones,and bots would have and how the wars started in more detail), and no im not trying to copy you. just to show how in some ways i would connect it, At the end of my story (if i could connect it with yours) i was going to write,<BR /> Epiloge...<BR />The New<BR /><BR />   Darkness hung over the world, not a sound on the whole of Crux. All was destroyed along with our hero and his freinds. In all they fought for it was in vain and now nothing could change the course of this fate, or could it?....... <BR />   <BR />All was not lost, for one day a brave minifigure would soon travle back to a different time on this forsaken planet and rock crux to its very core, unlock his destiny and find what he had looked for without knowing his entire life. The story of Crux has only begun. The end?............. <BR /><BR /> did you like it? Thanks for all you've done to help me. i hope you will somehow be able to tell me, but until then,<BR />yours truly, starwars7495 aka lightningwarrior95<BR /><BR />~life is a lego set, open the posibilities~<BR />
                
            
			
